separate boost and unboost, since unboost does not cap
flinch silently clears recharge - this is impl on showdown so we just don't know
binding ends silently, you need to parse the request for that

Request parsing:
reveals binding, reveals our own recharge status

Rage: if the target is immune we don't add the vol, but if it its already present then it doesn't matter

Trhashing: idfk what this is
